			<div>I am a Developer</div>
		</div>

		<div class={Styles.sectionText}>
			<p>
				Hello! My name is Bennjmann Redman you can call me Ben for short.
				Im a Developer who likes to work with a wide range of different technologies like high level languages such as Python to low level languages like C++ as well as use a wide range of frameworks like react or create games using engines like unity.
				I have a diverse range of knowledge over landscape of coding and want to explore even deeper.
			</p>
			<p>
				During my time working with these tool Iâ€™ve also picked up other skills like design and graphic design leading to developing skills with in tools adobe space of tools.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class={Styles.sectionContainer} id="projects">
			<h2>My projects and contributions</h2>
		</div>
		<div class={Styles.sectionContent}>
			<Card title="Project 1"/>
			<Card title="Project 2"/>
			<Card title="Project 3"/>
